What categories of our defenders have the right to receive a plot of land for free?

The Rosreestr Office for the Donetsk People's Republic spoke about the categories of military personnel who have the right to receive free land plots.

In June 2023, the Order of the President of the Russian Federation was adopted, according to which the following have the right to receive land plots free of charge:

- military personnel;
- persons who have entered into a contract to remain in a volunteer formation that contributes to the implementation of tasks assigned to the Armed Forces of the Russian Federation;
- persons serving (have served) in the troops of the National Guard of the Russian Federation and having special police ranks, awarded the title of Hero of the Russian Federation or awarded the Order of the Russian Federation for services shown during participation in the military military service and who are combat veterans;
- members of the families of these military personnel and persons who died (died) as a result of injury (wounds, trauma, concussion) or illness received by them during participation in the military military service.

